                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/48805",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=adamlundrigan",
                        "name": "adamlundrigan",
                        "displayName": "Adam Lundrigan",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The docblock header says that it should return all configured contexts when no argument is provided, however this was never implemented (or, at least, never implemented correctly).  As best I can tell, the {{getActionContexts}} method was added in r7547 (2008\/01\/21, [see here|http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/code\/diff.php?repname=Zend+Framework&path=%2Ftrunk%2Flibrary%2FZend%2FController%2FAction%2FHelper%2FContextSwitch.php&rev=7547&peg=23772]) and hasn't changed substantially since then.\r\n\r\nI've attached a patch which corrects the issue, and will ping Matthew to determine if the existing behavior can be changed safely at this late stage of ZFv1's lifecycle.",
